01:29.480 --> 01:30.524
I'm just saying.

01:30.548 --> 01:33.194
Could be depression from
your breakup with him,

01:33.219 --> 01:35.330
based on that song that I heard you sing

01:35.355 --> 01:37.234
that I don't know the
name of about your issues.

01:37.258 --> 01:38.609
- It was probably "Issues."
- You know what?

01:38.633 --> 01:40.577
I need to make sure
that everything's okay

01:40.602 --> 01:42.655
with my dad, my family.

01:42.680 --> 01:44.334
If there's a bad moon on the rise,

01:44.359 --> 01:46.405
maybe I can stop it before it's risen?

01:46.430 --> 01:48.428
Come on, buddy. Just a little bit more.

01:48.796 --> 01:50.101
Nah.

01:51.217 --> 01:53.195
Morning, Howie. Hi, Dad.

01:53.539 --> 01:55.069
How's he doing? Everything okay?

01:55.094 --> 01:58.241
- Nothing strange going on?
- No.

01:58.266 --> 02:00.378
