than normal this morning.

02:00.403 --> 02:04.090
Although, he was crushing me
in gin rummy earlier.

02:04.115 --> 02:06.436
I'm pretty sure he was cheating,

02:06.461 --> 02:08.761
although I'm still not sure how.

02:15.117 --> 02:16.628
I love you, too.

02:16.653 --> 02:18.663
Want to buzz me something in Morse code?

02:18.688 --> 02:21.038
