back to that one week

02:21.063 --> 02:22.707
when I was a Girl Scout before realizing

02:22.732 --> 02:24.991
I actually had to go camping
and be outside and stuff?

02:27.358 --> 02:29.000
Yeah, I figured.

02:29.196 --> 02:31.438
Aah! No, no, no, no, no!

02:31.463 --> 02:32.735
Damn it!

02:32.760 --> 02:34.032
Mom?

02:34.416 --> 02:35.789
- Ahh...
- Is everything okay?

02:35.814 --> 02:38.345
Yes, I dropped
my wedding ring down there

02:38.370 --> 02:40.939
and it's so dark, I can't see to get it.

02:42.253 --> 02:44.319
