02:44.703 --> 02:47.385
Sorry. Got it.

02:47.757 --> 02:51.088
Hey, did you notice
how chipper your dad is today?

02:51.113 --> 02:53.619
Yeah, he just laughed with me.

02:53.644 --> 02:56.728
