02:56.753 --> 02:59.487
Yeah. It's one of the good days.

03:10.230 --> 03:13.353
Well, well, well! Look who's back.

03:13.378 --> 03:15.408
Yeah, glad to be back.

03:15.433 --> 03:17.845
